des: "This is a super easy lemonade treat perfect for summer! I've made these many times, and they are so delicious. They're so easy, and they only have 1 ingredient!"
ins: Pour 3/4 cup lemonade into each ice pop cavity, leaving 1/2 inch clear at the top. Transfer ice pop tray carefully to the freezer. Freeze for 1 1/2 hour. Insert a popsicle stick into each ice pop. Freeze until solid, about 1 1/2 hour more.
